  "prob_desc_input_spec": "The first line contains one integer $$$n$$$ ($$$2 \\le n \\le 100$$$) — the number of digits in the ticket. The second line contains $$$n$$$ digits $$$a_1 a_2 \\dots a_n$$$ ($$$0 \\le a_i \\le 9$$$) — the golden ticket. Digits are printed without spaces.",
